    • classValidation

      public FitnessClass classValidation(FitnessClassType classtype, String instructor, Location location)
      method that takes user input and checks whether or not the class detailed by input corresponds to a real class in the class schedule. If the class queried is a real class, method will return a reference to the class in the ClassSchedule object. Otherwise, it will return null.
      Parameters:
      classtype - type of class being queried
      instructor - instructor for the class
      location - location at which class is taking place
      Returns:
      If the class exists in ClassSchedule return reference to the class, else return null
